name: RoboVox: Fish Pond
overview: RoboVox: Fish Pond (alternatively known as Fish Pond: RoboVox) is a shoot em up developed by Pinov Vox using the Shoot 'em Up Constriction Kit. The game was released as part of the 2020 SEUCK Competition. The main protagonist is somewhat inspired by the James Pond character from the James Pond series of platformers.
